data.description: This home has tiled floors throughout, garage converted to living area. Windows have accordion hurricane shutter, extended screen enclosed patio with spa tub. Back yard has many palm trees and storage shed. Interior has been freshly painted with new kitchen cabinets and master bath vanity. This home is in move-in ready condition. Home is conveniently located close to schools, park, shopping and major highways. This is a Fannie Mae Homepath property. 'First Time Buyers, complete the HomePath Ready Buyer homeownership course on homepath.com. Attach certificate to offer and request up to 3% closing cost assistance. Check HomePath.com for more details or ask me. Restrictions apply.' This is a Fannie Mae Homepath property
